       &kp C    &kp I               &kp A                &kp E                       &kp MINUS              &kp K          &kp H                &kp T            &kp N            &kp S
&kp B  &kp SQT  &mt LEFT_GUI COMMA  &mt LEFT_ALT PERIOD  &mt LEFT_CONTROL SEMICOLON  &kp SLASH              &kp J          &mt RIGHT_CONTROL M  &mt RIGHT_ALT G  &mt RIGHT_GUI P  &kp V  &kp F
